# MultiChat

Python CLI tool that sends the same message to multiple LLMs and returns their responses.

## Usage

Make sure to have at least one of the following API keys in your environment:

```bash
OPENAI_API_KEY
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
XAI_API_KEY
GEMINI_API_KEY
```

